title: Watch Dogs Hotfix-RELOADED
description:
Watch_Dogs *Hotfix* (c) Ubisoft

05/2014 :..... RELEASE.DATE .. PROTECTION .......: UbiDRM+Custom
DISC(S) .. GAME.TYPE ........: Action, Adventure

Note:

This is the Day 1 patch that was supposed to fix the most annoying game bugs.


1. Unrar.
2. Install the hotfix to dir where main game is installed.
3. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory to your game
install directory.
4. Play the game.
5. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
